    • StudySession

      public StudySession(String name, User creator, String subject, int classNumber, String location, String locationDetail) throws IllegalArgumentException
      Constructor for the StudySession object.
      Parameters:
      name - String, serves a unique identifier for StudySession
      creator - User, the creator user account
      subject - String identifying the subject
      classNumber - int, 4 digit number (is validated to 0 <= n <= 9999)
      location - String, building where study session is located
      locationDetail - String, details on where exactly the class is located in the building
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - thrown when a input is deemed invalid.
